メソッドの詳細

performRequest

NetworkResponse performRequest(Request<?> request)
                               throws VolleyError
Performs the specified request.

パラメータ:
request - Request to process
戻り値:
A NetworkResponse with data and caching metadata; will never be null
例外:
VolleyError - on errors
